item_description: Correct ocular artifact on the EEG during REM

steps.name: REMs corrector
steps.description: Ocular movement artifact corrector in REM

steps.name: Input Files
steps.description:
Select the .edf files to analyze.

Select the EEG channels to correct and add them in the EEG alias.

Select the EOG channels to base the correction on and add them in the EOG alias.

steps.name: Corrector Step
steps.description: Define the parameters for the corrector if different from default.

steps.name: Events to exclude
steps.description:
Select events to exclude from the PSA (i.e. artifacts).

Start by selecting one PSG or multiple files (with the ctrl key pressed), then select an event group or name.

Be aware that the files must still be highlighted in the GUI to apply the 'Select All' option.

steps.name: Validation Step
steps.description: Verify spectral power before and after the correction.
